      "content": "wait i thought you said pseudoephedrine isn't recommended in the first 20 weeks? im at 24 weeks now so i thought that meant it's safe for me since i'm past that window. if it's fine after 20 weeks, can i just take the usual dose of the pseudoephedrine i have? i really need the relief right now.",
